There has been an ongoing issue in the monk comunity considering that back when class balancing was discussed, the monks were left out and many of the things that were promised never came about (except a slight lowering of the weight on black panther armor).<br>
<br>
I'm not personally a huge supporter of the whiny types that are still screaming balance, but the monks and rogue community have actually gotten together and formed this open letter to Verant. The letter has some nice points and I think is worth supporting, if nothing else then just to see if Verant will do anything.<br>
<br>
